      "id": "fut2020",
      "index": "a160",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1328,
      "y": 338,
      "width": 440,
      "height": 80,
      "text": "Home:  db/  — BatBase client adapter (HTTP / SQL)\nAlso:   MetaResolver (APP LAYER) consumes drafts\n        batch/ may seed journals from BatBase\n        config/ holds URL + SecretStr credentials\nNot in: cellpycore (only meta scaffolding stays there)",
      "originalText": "Home:  db/  — BatBase client adapter (HTTP / SQL)\nAlso:   MetaResolver (APP LAYER) consumes drafts\n        batch/ may seed journals from BatBase\n        config/ holds URL + SecretStr credentials\nNot in: cellpycore (only meta scaffolding stays there)",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 2,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
