      "type": "text",
      "x": 1328,
      "y": 490,
      "width": 440,
      "height": 80,
      "text": "Home:  instruments/  — InstrumentLoader that queries\n        the tester DB (same contract as file loaders:\n        parse/query -> harmonize -> LoaderResult)\nAlso:   config/ for DSN/secrets; later utils/live for poll\nNot in: db/ (lab/meta journals, not cycler raw data)",
      "originalText": "Home:  instruments/  — InstrumentLoader that queries\n        the tester DB (same contract as file loaders:\n        parse/query -> harmonize -> LoaderResult)\nAlso:   config/ for DSN/secrets; later utils/live for poll\nNot in: db/ (lab/meta journals, not cycler raw data)",
      "fontSize": 12,
