      "index": "a170",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1328,
      "y": 642,
      "width": 440,
      "height": 110,
      "text": "Home:  exporters/  — entry-point exporter + layout spec\n        (file naming + folder structure for 4 layers)\nAlso:   batch/layout.py if export is batch-scoped\nNot in: cellpy_file/  — that is the native v9 cellpy\n        container (zip-of-parquet), a different product.\nCore:   only supplies the frames; naming/policy stay app.",
      "originalText": "Home:  exporters/  — entry-point exporter + layout spec\n        (file naming + folder structure for 4 layers)\nAlso:   batch/layout.py if export is batch-scoped\nNot in: cellpy_file/  — that is the native v9 cellpy\n        container (zip-of-parquet), a different product.\nCore:   only supplies the frames; naming/policy stay app.",
      "fontSize": 12,
      "fontFamily": 2,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
